Legend: The BBC pundit captained his country 34 times and scored 30 goals for the Three LIons

'You can make a mistake on a football pitch. You can't make a mistake on live TV - or you can but you might not get invited back.'

The Newcastle United legend also admitted that his son points out things he failed to notice on the show.

'As soon as I turn on my phone at midnight I have texts from my lad saying i should have said this or that. Or asking me why I was horrible about Newcastle. He doesn't like me criticising Newcastle.'

Opinions: Shearer admitted that he takes criticism from his own son when he criticises Newcastle 

